com.simiacryptus.mindseye.layers.cudnn

Class FullyConnectedLayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.NNLayer
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.layers.cudnn.FullyConnectedLayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LayerPrecision<FullyConnectedLayer>, Serializable

    public class FullyConnectedLayer
extends NNLayer
implements LayerPrecision<FullyConnectedLayer>
    A dense matrix operator using vector-matrix multiplication. Represents a fully connected layer of synapses, where all inputs are connected to all outputs via seperate coefficients.
    See Also:
